  "text": "The first goal of this note is to explain close relationships between the MV formula and the ELSV formula relating Hurwitz numbers H g,µ to Hodge integrals: [CITATION_1] H g,µ = (2g − 2 + |µ| + l(µ))! | Aut(µ)|",
